org.apache.cactus.internal
Class WebTestResult

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.cactus.internal.WebTestResult
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class WebTestResult
extends Object
implements Serializable

Represent the result of the execution of the Test class by the server redirector. If any exception was raised during the test, it is saved by this class.

Version:
$Id: WebTestResult.java 238991 2004-05-22 11:34:50Z vmassol $
